Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.66,0:03:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The great prison that holds villainous prisoners\Nfrom all over the world - Impel Down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.70,0:03:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's greatest prison - so heavily \Nguarded - has just been breached!
