Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.14,0:03:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,there was a man who had broken \Nout of the iron-tight Impel Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.72,0:03:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real! He cut off his own legs!
