Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain! Colt-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.26,0:05:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.82,0:05:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have word from Big Boss Shiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.93,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, finally! We've waited so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.30,0:05:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Bring a Transponder Snail here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.46,0:05:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.46,0:05:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, we did it! If we \Ncan join Shiki's party,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,it's gonna be our chance \Nto become successful!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Big Bro? Why are you crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.52,0:06:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Amore! My beloved brother Colt!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.31,0:06:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I am very sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.81,0:06:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If the plan of senor \NShiki is put into action,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.70,0:06:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the world will be filled with sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,When I think about hearing \Nthousands of despairing voices,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.46,0:06:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it makes me very very sad...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is a Transponder Snail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.16,0:06:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! Put him through!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you the captain of \NAmigo Pirates - Mr. Largo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm First Mate Colt. \NTell me what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.23,0:06:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.31,0:06:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I called to let you know that we have decided
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,to welcome Mr. Largo to Big \NBoss Shiki's assembly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...as our 51st pirate captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,--No surprise there!\N--However...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...there is a condition to \Nyour attending the assembly
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and we need to ask you to fulfill that first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Conditions?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.69,0:07:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing so far...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,No good at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You look pretty full to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been having banquets \Nevery night these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So our stomachs have expanded and \Nwe have to eat more to be satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.15,0:07:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right! It feels like my \Nbones are bigger these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.56,0:07:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How's it going? Catch something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not good! Not even a nibble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.51,0:07:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We're totally out of food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't catch anything, \Nit'll be no food for you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.96,0:08:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't "what?!" me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.82,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it was a bad idea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.40,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,to have a banquet before \Nwe got to the next island!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.70,0:08:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But you guys were...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.26,0:08:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Banquet! Banquet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.63,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how we were?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't even remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A bite! I've got something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Way to go, Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.04,0:08:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.98,0:08:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! We're gonna have \Nanother banquet tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.60,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch that fish even if it kills you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,--Banquet!\N--Hang on! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.45,0:08:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.44,0:09:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.27,0:09:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.35,0:09:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's a...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.52,0:09:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...He ate it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.15,0:09:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.29,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.80,0:10:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...a pirate ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.32,0:10:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What shameless bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.73,0:10:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's coming back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a big beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.70,0:10:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna ride on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you nuts, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.03,0:10:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Usopp! Let's catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.14,0:10:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Where the hell did you get that net?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not gonna let it destroy our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Coup de Vent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.92,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Franky's attack didn't work?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.80,0:11:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, come on, you giant beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.99,0:11:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.91,0:11:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...Bazooka!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They blew Boss away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:50.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That beetle breathes fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna roast our ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.38,0:11:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! You alright?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.14,0:12:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That beetle isn't just \Nhuge - he breathes fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.51,0:12:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How cool is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.12,0:12:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.07,0:12:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.36,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm gonna make him one of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.03,0:12:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! No! Wait a minute, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.27,0:12:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you giant beetle! Join my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.03,0:12:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he doing there?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they seem to be getting bigger...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,He's aiming at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.41,0:12:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Help... Help...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.29,0:12:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:13:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,--Oh no, Usopp!\N--Damn it! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.78,0:13:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's flying away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What were they thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.49,0:13:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, look! An island!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.12,0:13:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that where the beetle came from?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.57,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out, Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.83,0:13:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! We're gonna hit the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.08,0:14:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't get away now, you giant beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.65,0:14:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give up and become one of my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.65,0:14:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't take "no" for an answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.28,0:14:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.49,0:14:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,...will never become...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.75,0:14:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.55,0:14:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.51,0:14:29.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow! What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know there was an island like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...What the hell is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko! What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful! He's a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.03,0:14:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,A pirate?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Show us mercy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.05,0:14:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are Straw Hats, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.69,0:15:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.98,0:15:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah! He's a Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.14,0:15:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! He's "Pirate Hunter" Zoro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.56,0:15:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's "Black Leg" Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.02,0:15:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.94,0:15:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! He tried to steal Boss from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.64,0:15:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna bite you to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yoko! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and just let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! You are the owner of this beetle?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.17,0:15:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The owner?! No way! Boss is my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.20,0:15:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you're already on someone else's team?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.01,0:15:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any way that you'd let me have him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.44,0:15:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not! Over my dead body!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! I give him up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.47,0:16:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.32,0:16:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.48,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry if I hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.02,0:16:35.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that you defeated him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.89,0:16:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey!\N--Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,These wounds mean nothing to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.84,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll heal up overnight while \Nhe's sleeping underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not only that! Tomorrow he will molt!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.07,0:16:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll become bigger and stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.91,0:17:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do they continue doing that \Neven as full grown beetles?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss is different. He sheds \Nhis skin once a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.97,0:17:11.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why he's so big.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.05,0:17:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna be stronger than you are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.76,0:17:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, he is! What do you say to that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.40,0:17:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Then, let's have \Nthis fight again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.49,0:17:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's make it clear which \None of us is stronger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so silly... Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! So I have your word, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.24,0:17:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He is an interesting young man as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What a big cave! What is it for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.02,0:18:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an escape route.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.02,0:18:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Escape route?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This cave is like a maze.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.26,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can escape through this \Ncave when pirates come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We are world champions at \Nrunning away and groveling!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.04,0:18:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're proud of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we survive in the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.16,0:18:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have a military \Nand it's a remote island
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.48,0:18:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so the Navy always leaves \Nus on a back burner.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Speaking about the Navy, that \Ngirl was wearing a Navy coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.86,0:18:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there any reason for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.39,0:18:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,She wears it in memory of her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He was a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.28,0:18:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He couldn't stand by and see us \Nrepeatedly attacked by pirates
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.41,0:18:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,so he stayed on this island separated from
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.06,0:18:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,other marines in order to protect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.00,0:18:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "in memory of" so I assume...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.81,0:19:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It was exactly five years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.66,0:19:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,he was fighting against some \Npirates alone and died.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.67,0:19:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Three years later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.19,0:19:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss came to us out of nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.96,0:19:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He bonded with Yoko right away and became
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,the guardian angel of this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.08,0:19:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe, Boss reminds her of her \Nlate father who was strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay for us to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.32,0:19:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You people are different! Now, we are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! A windmill! It's gigantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.67,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so high!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.24,0:20:05.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I thought that it was just a \Ncrag but it's beautiful in the back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.57,0:20:07.92,Default,,0,0,0,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.92,0:20:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How can I say this? The buildings \Nhere are all different in style...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.24,0:20:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a strange town!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.36,0:20:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a deserted island when we first
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,got here and that was just the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Since then, for some reason, people \Nare coming here from the same ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what made this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.73,0:20:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Straw Hats!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Kansorn Island where people \Nfrom the East Blue live together!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.32,0:20:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It also known as Little East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.43,0:20:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! I didn't expect to see the rookie \Nof great promise in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro-san! You're from \NFrost Moon Village, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a training hall for \Npeople who came from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.08,0:20:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come and see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.16,0:20:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A training hall?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.81,0:20:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji-san, you grew up on The Baratie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.30,0:21:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Try the food at the local Baratie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.58,0:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You have The Baratie here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.07,0:21:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone from Syrup Village?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.85,0:21:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I think Luigia is from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.45,0:21:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Luigia?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.77,0:21:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. She's living in the most \Nluxurious mansion in this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mansion? The only mansion in \NSyrup Village is Kaya's mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! Everybody's so caught up in them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.00,0:21:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Pirates are all the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.61,0:21:32.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder how they're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.88,0:21:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Chopper! They'll call us soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.72,0:21:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.02,0:21:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We better get an insect cage fixed for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. If the beetle \Njoins us, we will need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.85,0:21:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's me! Is Nami there?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.79,0:21:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Usopp? It's me! What's \Nwrong? Did you catch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.08,0:21:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No no no, it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.77,0:22:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.13,0:22:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I'm wondering - can you come over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.68,0:22:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a town on the \Nother side of the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.22,0:22:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that they really wanna see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.22,0:22:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Call her "Nami-sama"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.35,0:22:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.47,0:22:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just come over here! I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.23,0:22:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,He hung up!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.44,0:22:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do they want just Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.47,0:22:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.36,0:22:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.12,0:22:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the ship to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.11,0:22:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Count on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.25,0:22:41.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There she goes...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.12,0:22:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rockbound and there \Nare reefs all around it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.40,0:22:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so regular ships can't approach the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.04,0:22:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, reefs are no problem with this ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's go hunting!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.53,0:23:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna get the big beetle that \Ntook off from Shiki's hide-out!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.28,0:23:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.31,0:23:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats arrive at the island\Nwhere immigrants from the East Blue live.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.72,0:23:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,The scenery looks so much like their homeland\Nthat they can't help but reminisce.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.50,0:23:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the Amigo Pirates are also heading toward\Nthe island in pursuit of the giant beetle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.47,0:23:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,"Movie Tie-in Special\NLittle East Blue in Danger"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.14,0:23:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
